description: This source file defines Express.js route handlers for the notes API, including CRUD operations such as listing, retrieving, creating, updating, and deleting notes. It also contains Swagger documentation annotations for API documentation.

methods.name: router.get
methods.description: Handles GET requests to list all notes, with optional search filtering.

methods.name: router.get('/:id')
methods.description: Handles GET requests to retrieve a specific note by ID.

methods.name: router.post
methods.description: Handles POST requests to create a new note.

methods.name: router.put('/:id')
methods.description: Handles PUT requests to update an existing note by ID.

methods.name: router.delete('/:id')
methods.description: Handles DELETE requests to delete a note by ID.
